    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone prioritizing function over aesthetics. The engine starts reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring it gets you from point A to point B without issue. However, potential buyers should be aware of several cosmetic imperfections, including minor dents on the passenger side door, some fading in the clear coat on the hood, and visible wear on the driver's seat upholstery. It has been regularly maintained mechanically, though it lacks the pristine look of a newer model. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for reliable transportation at a reasonable price.",
