    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an exacting standard that defies its tenure. The vehicle remains in a state of absolute preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original showroom integrity. Subjected to a comprehensive multi-point technical evaluation, this automobile performs with the precision and vigor of a new delivery. For the individual who accepts only the superlative, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality.",
      "price": 48900.0,
